{"tid":1036255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Steam《還願》銷售突破100萬套！《返校》受惠同登暢銷榜","createTime":"2019-02-25T06:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T06:16:15.000Z","uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52a239a0bc53aee879da989b203062dbae847953","tid":1036255,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:13:16.000Z","msg":"由赤燭遊戲開發的新作《還願 Devotion》，雖因遊戲中「維尼符咒」爭議身陷發行商切割求償與中國抵制風波，不過在台灣玩家社群與國際媒體發酵下，銷售區間已在 Steamspy 正式踏入 100 萬套區間，也在近日連霸 Steam 暢銷榜榜首。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n根據 Steamspy 付費會員介面資料，《還願》在銷售數字的估值已來到 1,122,000 套，符合未登入會員所看到的 100 至 200 萬套區間，這也顯示出台灣玩家社群力挺赤燭遊戲的驚人力量。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/Why%20Lee/News/2019.02/388709a45146d5142754cc3d3ab8659d.png?versionId=yTySX.qvAs15k5M9lmP6SAmX5YzrOGPm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FWhy%2520Lee%2FNews%2F2019.02%2F388709a45146d5142754cc3d3ab8659d.png%3FversionId%3DyTySX.qvAs15k5M9lmP6SAmX5YzrOGPm&h=22c229dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同時，在 Steam 暢銷榜中《還願》不僅已連霸榜首多日，就連赤燭團隊 2017 的作品《返校 Detention》也因而受惠，在 Steamspy 紀錄區間已來到 50 萬套區間，詳細數字已至 62.7 萬套。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/TangBao/1902/25-detention-01.jpg?versionId=v811iRmSuzSTBLT2HyoMP.iF8yW4HLgG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FTangBao%2F1902%2F25-detention-01.jpg%3FversionId%3Dv811iRmSuzSTBLT2HyoMP.iF8yW4HLgG&h=ff442cae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自推出後，《還願》在日本 IGN 獲得 9.8 高分的好評，同時歐美知名遊戲媒體 Eurogamer、PC Gamer 也相繼報導中國封殺《還願》消息，更是助長赤燭遊戲的國際聲量。<br />\n<br />\n此外，繼行政院副院長陳其邁在 Facebook 宣布支持，現預計 2 月 25 日晚間 20:00 實況遊玩《還願》，預期將帶出另一波高潮。"},{"pid":"b530fcfc25f9704098882071a163d2a75707e4ac","tid":1036255,"uid":46500,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"個防老翻水印真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}